data.title: Eric Shinseki's career
data.meta_description: President George W. Bush (center) talks with the chiefs of staff of the armed forces after a meeting in the Cabinet Room on Oct. 23, 2001, at the White House. From left are Adm. Richard Mies, Gen. Eric Shinseki, Gen. Pete Pace and Gen. Michael Williams.
